Logix Gateway Bridge (LGB)
Copyright 2026 Carlos Fontán and contributors.

LGB is an open source bidirectional gateway between Rockwell ControlLogix and
CompactLogix programmable logic controllers and modern IIoT standards
(OPC UA, MQTT Sparkplug B).

This product includes software developed by the LGB project.
Project repository: https://github.com/fgjcarlos/lgb

